{
  "id": "69a49d5f426efe37981c7cde",
  "title": "「人間の相対性」",
  "created": 1772395873,
  "updated": 1772397242,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a49d5f426efe37981c7cde",
      "text": "「人間の相対性」",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772395873,
      "updated": 1772396220
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49e2c00000000009ec610",
      "text": "[/ [The Dual Nature of Man]] by [Aušra Augustinavičiūtė]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396077,
      "updated": 1772396088
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49fbb00000000009ec627",
      "text": "Published in [/ Journal \"[Socionics, Mentology and Personality Psychology]\", [1996], N 1-3]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396475,
      "updated": 1772396535
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49fcb00000000009ec62d",
      "text": "#ソシオニクス の創案者の初期の著作",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396491,
      "updated": 1772396816
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49d6000000000009ec5fe",
      "text": "英訳：[https://wikisocion.github.io/en/index.php@title=The_Dual_Nature_of_Man.html Wikisocion] [\" This translation was done by an automatic translator.]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772395873,
      "updated": 1772397196
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49e6300000000009ec617",
      "text": "日本語訳：by [https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html From Over the Sea]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396132,
      "updated": 1772396280
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49e7400000000009ec618",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396148,
      "updated": 1772396148
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ecb00000000009ec619",
      "text": "要約とメモ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396236,
      "updated": 1772396953
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ed000000000009ec61b",
      "text": "\t人間には、いわゆる「相性の良い人々の類型」と「相性の悪い人々の類型」がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396241,
      "updated": 1772396451
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ecc00000000009ec61a",
      "text": "\t人の相性を理解するための類型としては、ユングの[『タイプ論』]が最も適している",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396236,
      "updated": 1772396436
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a02700000000009ec62e",
      "text": "\t> 筆者から付け加えると、人間のタイプは精神的なものだけでなく、身体的な疾患の傾向も左右します。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396584,
      "updated": 1772396595
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f7b00000000009ec626",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396411,
      "updated": 1772396598
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a03500000000009ec62f",
      "text": "\tユングの用語が情報代謝理論の要素に完全に一致しているわけではない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396597,
      "updated": 1772396657
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a07d00000000009ec631",
      "text": "\tユングの用語のうち、〈思考〉(Thinking) と〈感情〉(Feeling) は誤解を招く表現であるため、ソシオニクスにおいてはこれを〈論理〉〈倫理〉と呼称する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396670,
      "updated": 1772396796
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a14200000000009ec636",
      "text": "\t\tNote: ここでオーシュラは[\" 思考タイプは客観的なことについて、後者は自分たちを取り巻く世界について、主観的に思考している]としている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396867,
      "updated": 1772397009
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a25f00000000009ec63b",
      "text": " \t\t現代のソシオニクスにおいてもこの解釈には異論がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772397152,
      "updated": 1772397156
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a18b00000000009ec637",
      "text": " \t\t元々のユングの二分法において〈客観的〉〈主観的〉と対応させられているのは、〈外向的〉と〈内向的〉の[二項対立]である",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396940,
      "updated": 1772397242
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a0b100000000009ec634",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396722,
      "updated": 1772396723
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a0b200000000009ec635",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396723,
      "updated": 1772396723
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ee400000000009ec61c",
      "text": "依拠するもの",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396261,
      "updated": 1772396372
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49eed00000000009ec61e",
      "text": "\t[ピョートル・ガヌシュキン]（П. Б. Ганнушкина）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396269,
      "updated": 1772396320
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ef100000000009ec61f",
      "text": "\t[エルンスト・クレッチマー]（Kretschmer）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396274,
      "updated": 1772396310
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f1600000000009ec622",
      "text": "\t\t[クレッチマーの気質類型]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396311,
      "updated": 1772396316
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ef400000000009ec620",
      "text": "\t[カール・グスタフ・ユング] (C.G. Jung)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396276,
      "updated": 1772396332
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49efb00000000009ec621",
      "text": "\tA.[ケンピンスキー]（А. Кемпинского）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396284,
      "updated": 1772396330
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f3500000000009ec625",
      "text": "\t\t[情報代謝理論]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396342,
      "updated": 1772396348
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f2900000000009ec623",
      "text": "\t[アンドレイ・リチコ]（А. Е. Личко）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396330,
      "updated": 1772396338
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f2d00000000009ec624",
      "text": "\t[カール・レオンハルト]（K. Leonhard）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396334,
      "updated": 1772396336
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ee500000000009ec61d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396262,
      "updated": 1772396262
    }
  ]
}